<p>
    2015 was the year of <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Expo_2015">Expo</a> in Milan.<br>
    After a few weeks, my friend Davide Trezzi and I came up with the idea of letting the visitors rank the pavillions using a
    friendly and fun-to-use user interface. We decided to use the ELO ranking system, which is the same algorithm that
    Mark Zuckerberg used for his facemash.com, as described in the movie "The Social Network".
</p>
